1. The "Dot" Legend
Think of your file explorer as a map, and these symbols as your current GPS location:
    ./ (One Dot): "The folder I am currently in."
    ../ (Two Dots): "Go back one folder (Up to the parent)."
    ../../ (Four Dots): "Go back two folders."

